cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.DC, cs.NE, cs.AI. 

The paper proposes a new approach for multi-GPU DNN training, which is a common topic in machine learning and computer vision research. Therefore, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses the weight inconsistency and staleness issues incurred by asynchronous pipeline parallelism, which are related to distributed computing and parallel processing, suggesting cs.DC as another likely sub-category. Additionally, the paper proposes a novel weight prediction strategy, which involves machine learning techniques, making cs.NE and cs.AI also possible sub-categories.
